How does one set an avatar in the first place? I can't see any option to do that anywhere. Does one have to be subscribed to all of the NYT rather than just NYT Games to do that?

Also, Swiss roll... I googled it to discover it has nothing to do with Switzerland and the name's origins are unknown. We have such inexplicably named dishes in Poland, too, like Breton beans (fasolka po bretońsku) and Greek fish (ryba po grecku) - neither has any relation to Breton or Greek cuisine.

